HEADWORD: Soapy
<hw>Soap"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Soapier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
